Pour mettre à jour phpMyAdmin :

1- Dans le fichier config.inc.php, ajouter les la config de single sign on :
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['auth_type'] = 'signon';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['SignonSession'] = 'AutomneSession';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['SignonURL']     = 'atmAuth.php';

2- dans le fichier libraires/auth/signon.auth.lib.php, dans la fonction PMA_auth_check(), ligne 128, ajouter les lignes de limitation de la base à voir :
//Added for Automne : Do not remove
//set the database name to connect
if (isset($_SESSION['PMA_single_signon_only_db'])) {
	$GLOBALS['cfg']['Server']['only_db']=$_SESSION['PMA_single_signon_only_db'];
}
//End Added for Automne : Do not remove

3- A la racine de phpMyAdmin, ajouter les fichiers .htaccess et atmAuth.php

4- rename file (path too long) :
phpMyAdmin/libraries/PHPExcel/PHPExcel/Shared/Escher/DggContainer/BstoreContainer/BSE/Blip.php
into :
phpMyAdmin/libraries/PHPExcel/PHPExcel/Shared/Escher/DggContainer/BstoreContainer/BSE/B.php
and rename all class name reference PHPExcel_Shared_Escher_DggContainer_BstoreContainer_BSE_Blip into PHPExcel_Shared_Escher_DggContainer_BstoreContainer_BSE_B

5- rename file (path too long) :
phpMyAdmin/libraries/PHPExcel/PHPExcel/Shared/Escher/DgContainer/SpgrContainer/SpContainer.php
into :
phpMyAdmin/libraries/PHPExcel/PHPExcel/Shared/Escher/DgContainer/SpgrContainer/SpCont.php
and rename all class name reference PHPExcel_Shared_Escher_DgContainer_SpgrContainer_SpContainer into PHPExcel_Shared_Escher_DgContainer_SpgrContainer_SpCont

6- Remove useless folders :
	- phpMyAdmin/documentation-gsoc
	- phpMyAdmin/themes/darkblue_orange
	- phpMyAdmin/setup
	- phpMyAdmin/contrib
	- phpMyAdmin/lang/* except english-utf-8.inc.php and french-utf-8.inc.php files
	